{"tid":605035,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"70款麵任選　即食麵主題餐廳走紅","createTime":"2018-03-25T09:42:09.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-25T09:47:08.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"9ba8b8a9002552e664fdee13bce56e25b0410d07","tid":605035,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:42:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180325/20342251\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342251&d=pA7LzFYulaAqKx0ipF9zebZGMQxn7aheim1dKZ3ASAU%3D&h=823e6de8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180325%2F20342251&h=4b4c3956\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180325/20342251</a><br />\n<br />\n70款麵任選　即食麵主題餐廳走紅<br />\n<br />\n兩岸要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180325/large/25cb3p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180325%2Flarge%2F25cb3p.jpg&h=5c933f48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即食麵主題餐廳成打卡熱點，客人在店內揀選即食麵。<br />\n<br />\n「你愛我清風醉酒，我卻獨愛烈風自由。」這是一家位於福建廈門思明東路「泡麵小食堂」主題餐廳門口的標語，它已成為當地一家網紅店，吸引無數年輕人或遊客慕名而來。這家由90後女生經營的主題餐廳，提供了70多種來自世界各地，如日本、韓國、香港、台灣和印尼、馬來西亞等不同種類的即食麵，顧客先在牆上挑選，廚師就會烹調出美味的即食麵。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n女店主：分享吃麵情懷<br />\n<br />\n雖說多吃即食麵無益，美國大學早年亦針對南韓人食用即食麵研究顯示，常吃即食麵民眾易罹患心血管疾病或中風，且以女性族群罹病較多。但90後女店主表示，自己喜歡旅遊，喜歡吃世界各地的即食麵，就想「分享即食麵的味道和情懷」，因此就開了這家專門煮即食麵的主題餐廳，每天接待顧客的數量約300位，有本地的，也有不少遊客。 <br />\n<br />\n多維新聞網/VCG/美國《Yahoo Health》<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180325/large/25cb4p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180325%2Flarge%2F25cb4p.jpg&h=38f25281&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n即食麵賣相吸引。"},{"pid":"9f7dacd0e6ef76613222c4885e845e12449be943","tid":605035,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:44:30.000Z","msg":"https://<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">hk</span>.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20180325/20342251"},{"pid":"e3f6498d8e8c0f12b42501bc85cb7360d23bd219","tid":605035,"uid":19552,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-25T09:47:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20060902/large/02la8p2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20060902%2Flarge%2F02la8p2.jpg&h=84e90c02&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}